https://github.com/sipeed/sigrok_slogic
Branch: hardware-sipeed-slogic-analyzer-support

Build-system glue to register the Sipeed SLogic logic analyzer
driver. The driver sources live in FILESDIR (copied in src_prepare)
to keep this patch under the pkgcheck FileSize limit.

diff --git a/Makefile.am b/Makefile.am
